Takatarisana ne[[Kubika kweZimbabwe]] (Zimbabwean Cuisine),[[manhuchu]] (samp in English) zvinoreva chibage chinodzvurwa chigofashaidzwa kusvika chaibva. Kana chigage chadzvura rukanda rwekunze rwaipuruka kubva, chibage chozopepetwa kuti marara aya araswe.

Mukubikwa kwe[[manhuchu]] anorungwa ne[[munyu]] kana kuzowedzera dovi. Nguva zhinji manhuchu chikafu chinodyiwa masikati vanhu vari pabasa.
